question:
What will be the output of the following code?

```cpp
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    int x = 10;
    cout << ++x * x;
}
```

What will be the output of the following code?

```cpp
#include <iostream>
#include <vector>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    vector<int> v = {1,2,3};
    cout << v.at(3);
}
```

